data.description:
10K PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! Sellers are also offering a 5,000 dollar credit with acceptable offer, that can help with closing costs or used to buy down your rate! 
MUST SEE!! Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage home, located in a wonderful neighborhood in Copperas Cove. This spacious single story home offers over 2,000 square feet with a great floor plan including, a large living room with a corner wood burning fireplace and open views of the kitchen and formal dining. This home also offers the master bedroom located on the opposite side of the home from the other bedrooms. You will also love the big backyard great for entertaining with a covered back porch and full privacy fence and an added storage building. Schedule a showing and come see everything this property has to offer. Please have you or your agent verify all specifics including measurements and square footage.
